description: Hairdressers, cinemas and places of worship are among businesses that will be allowed to reopen.
title: Coronavirus: Jersey to further ease lockdown from 12 June
title_page: Coronavirus: Jersey to further ease lockdown from 12 June - BBC News
maintext: He said: "This is evidence that our 'contain, delay and shield' strategy has so far thankfully proved the worst predictions wrong and enabled us to protect islanders' health, particularly those members of our society who are most vulnerable."
